\\\Rightarrow\qquad\left(\sqrt[3]{\frac{2x+M}{N}}\right)^3&=\left(2\sqrt[3]{\frac{x+M}{N}}\right)^3
\\\Rightarrow\qquad \frac{2x+M}{N}&=\frac{8(x+M)}{N}
